# Road Accident Dashboard (Excel)

## Project Overview  
This project analyzes a **large-scale accident dataset** (over **300k+ rows, 20+ columns**) using **Excel PivotTables** and visualization tools.  
The goal was to identify accident trends, severity distribution, and high-risk factors to support road safety analysis.  

## Features  
- **Casualty Analysis**: Fatal, serious, and slight casualties.  
- **Trend Tracking**: Year-over-year monthly accident comparisons.  
- **Vehicle Type Insights**: Cars, motorcycles, trucks, buses, and more.  
- **Geographical Breakdown**: Rural vs. urban, road type, and surface conditions.  
- **Time-Based Analysis**: Day vs. night accident trends.  
- **Filter Panel**: Interactive slicers for accident year, area type, and conditions.  

## Tools Used  
- Microsoft Excel  
  - PivotTables  
  - PivotCharts  
  - Slicers for filtering  
  - Large dataset handling  

